# Model-eval artifacts: imported course corpora, page renders, predictions, metrics.
# The harness itself (scripts/model-eval/) IS tracked — only its inputs/outputs are not.
# These MUST stay out of git: the corpus is real Canvas course content (instructor
# names, third-party course material), and a run is ~60MB of PNGs.
/.frugal-fable/
/eval-runs/
/eval-corpus/
